.DT
colour
Discworld concepts
colour

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
To enable colour you need to set your terminal type using the 'term'
command.  You can then configure the colours that messages are
displayed in with the 'colours' command.  You can also use the 'options'
command.

See the specific helpfiles on each command.
.EP

.SH See also
.SI 5
term, colours, options, rows, cols, resize, zmud_colours
.EI
